Hello everyone,

Here is CORE 2062’s 2023 code release. We’ve been working on a number of different projects throughout the season and into the off-season, so I’m going to be posting links to each of the repositories here.

First, we have our 2023 code:

core2062/CORE2023

Secondly, we have our CORERobotLib:

core2062/CORERobotLib

Third we have our scouting system:

core2062/COREScouting

Fourth we have our command based 2022 testing code:

core2062/CORE-Command-Based

Fifth we have swerve drive:

core2062/CORE-2022-Swerve

Sixth we have our update code for our 2022 robot:

core2062/CORE-2022

Seventh we have our basic swerve robot code:

core2062/PitDisplay

Questions and comments are welcome!
